,insight_fifty_detail_nameless:"League average is around 35%.",insight_pocket_text:e=>`Heavy pocket — ${e} players delay, shooting lanes`,insight_pocket_detail:"They shoot heavy break lanes. Priority: survive the start, don't run through paint.",insight_conservative_text:e=>`Slow tempo — ${e} runner${e===1?"":"s"} on the break`,insight_conservative_detail:"Slow pace. Get alive first, then build pressure from angles — the tape opens up.",insight_agg_start_text:e=>`Aggressive break — ${e} go on the buzzer`,insight_agg_start_detail:"They send many runners on break. Disciplined lanes will catch them in the open.",insight_dorito_dominant_text:e=>`Dorito-heavy — ${e}% of points`,insight_dorito_dominant_detail:"Their main side. Snake will be under-defended — send a player there.",insight_snake_dominant_text:e=>`Snake-heavy — ${e}% of points`,insight_snake_dominant_detail:"Their main side. Dorito will be under-defended — send a player there.",insight_side_vuln_text:(e,t)=>`Loses points when attacked through ${e} — ${t}% of losses`,insight_side_vuln_detail:e=>`We win ${e}% when we attack that side. Keep pressuring there.`,insight_center_text:e=>`Controls center in ${e}% of points`,insight_center_detail:"They dominate center — limit crossfires and respect the mid player.",insight_uncovered_text:e=>`They don't shoot toward ${e} during obstacle play`,insight_uncovered_detail:e=>`A player entering through ${e} will meet minimal resistance.`,insight_player_strong_text:e=>`Key player makes a big difference (+${e}% win rate when playing)`,insight_player_strong_detail:(e,t,n)=>`With them: ${e}% wins. Without: ${t}% (${n} pts).`,insight_player_weak_text:e=>`One player drags the team (${e}%)`,insight_player_weak_detail:(e,t,n)=>`With them: ${e}% wins vs ${t}% without (${n} pts).`,insight_late_break_text:e=>`Secondary push after break — ${e}% of points`,insight_late_break_detail:"They send a player a moment after the buzzer. Hold lanes active for a few seconds.",insight_predictable_text:e=>`Predictable — same setup in ${e}% of points`,insight_predictable_detail:(e,t,n)=>`${e} of ${t} points: ${n}. Prep a specific counter.`,insight_unpredictable_text:e=>`Unpredictable — ${e} different break setups`,insight_unpredictable_detail:e=>`No setup dominates (max ${e}%). Play solid fundamentals, not one counter.`,formation_on_dorito:e=>`${e} on dorito`,formation_on_snake:e=>`${e} on snake`,formation_in_center:e=>`${e} in center`,counter_fifty_action:e=>`Hold lanes on the ${e} side`,counter_fifty_detail:e=>`They push the fifty aggressively via ${e}. Set a player to hold the lane and kill the runner before they reach the fifty.`,counter_pocket_action:"Survive the break — read their lanes",counter_pocket_detail:"They have 4+ players shooting from the base. Don't run through paint — wait for a reload or quiet moment, then attack the open tape.",counter_conservative_action:"Get alive, then apply pressure",counter_conservative_detail:"They play slow. Get alive on good bunkers first, then build pressure from the angles. Don't force the break.",counter_agg_start_action:"Lanes on break — free eliminations",counter_agg_start_detail:"They send many runners. Disciplined lanes off the buzzer rack up eliminations before they reach their bunkers.",counter_attack_snake_action:"Attack snake — it's exposed",counter_attack_snake_detail:"They focus on dorito. Send an aggressive player to snake — minimal resistance.",counter_attack_dorito_action:"Attack dorito — it's exposed",counter_attack_dorito_detail:"They focus on snake. Send an aggressive player to dorito — minimal resistance.",counter_side_vuln_action:e=>`Pressure through ${e} — that's where they bleed`,counter_side_vuln_detail:"Most of their losses come from this side. Repeat the attack.",counter_center_action:"Challenge their mid player",counter_center_detail:"They dominate center. Send a mid player with good lane coverage — force them to respect it.",counter_uncovered_action:e=>`Send a runner through ${e} — nobody shoots there`,counter_uncovered_detail:"This side is consistently uncovered during obstacle play. The runner will walk through unopposed.",counter_player_action:"Eliminate their key player on the break",counter_player_detail:"Without them their results drop significantly. Focus fire at the start of the point.",counter_predictable_action:"Counter their predictable setup",counter_pred_detail_nobody:"Nobody runs to tape. Your front players can enter both sides safely — the only threat is mid lanes.",counter_pred_detail_no_dorito:"They don't play dorito. Your D-front can push deep safely. Set a lane on their snake player.",counter_pred_detail_no_snake:"They don't play snake. Your snake can enter unopposed. Set a lane on their dorito player.",counter_pred_detail_same:e=>`Same setup in ${e}% of points. Prep a specific counter setup before the match.`,counter_unpredictable_action:"Play solid fundamentals",counter_unpredictable_detail:"They rotate setups — no single counter will work. Focus on lane discipline and communication.",counter_late_break_action:"Hold lanes past the buzzer",counter_late_break_detail:"They send a player a few seconds after the start, once others have entered position. Stay in lane for 3–4 seconds past the buzzer.",attendees_title:"Attendees",squads_title:"Squads",matches_title:"Matches",add_short:"+ Add",add_match:"+ Add match",tap_to_scout:"tap to scout",no_matches:"No matches yet",set_up_squads:"Set up squads",new_matchup:"New matchup",home_squad:"Home squad",away_squad:"Away squad",select_ph:"— select —",coach_notes:"Coach notes",note_ph:"e.g. Dykta shoots Snake50...",no_notes:"No notes yet — add your observations",notes_hint:"Notes are saved to layout — visible in tournament prep too",notes_no_layout:"Assign a layout to this training to enable notes",delete_note:"Delete note?",players_title:"Players",pts_matchups:(e,t)=>`${e} pts · ${t} matchups`,training_section:"Training",attendees_sub:e=>`${e} players present`,squads_sub_empty:"Not set up",layo